[Additional Edge TTS Parameters] ### Adjusting speed, pitch, volume

```json5
{
  "messages": {
    "tts": {
      "edge": {
        "voice": "en-US-JennyNeural",
        "lang": "en-US",
        "rate": "+10%",      // Speed: -50% to +100%
        "pitch": "-5%",     // Pitch: -50% to +50%
        "volume": "+5%"     // Volume: -100% to +100%
      }
    }
  }
}
```

